logentry-massmessage-send:
$3 here is the title of a page containing a list of recipients, so an example log entry would look like "Legoktm sent a message to Wikipedia:Wikipedia Signpost/Subscriptions (Signpost for Aug 14, 2013)".
----
{{logentry}}

logentry-massmessage-send-page-message:
$3 is the title of a page containing a list of recipients, $5 is the page that was sent as a message. so an example log entry would look like "Legoktm sent page WikiPage as message to Wikipedia:Wikipedia Signpost/Subscriptions (Signpost for Jun 21, 2021)".
----
{{logentry}}

logentry-massmessage-failure:
{{logentry}}
* $4 is the subject line of the message
* $5 is the API error code. This will always be in English.

